## What happened

## Version information

Flutter 2.2.3 • channel stable • https://github.com/flutter/flutter.git

Engine • revision 241c87ad80

comment_data.body: The reason was flutter console being in the beta channel, causing flutter to not upgrade to latest version. Fix was flutter channel dev then flutter upgrade in console.
Great, glad you found a fix! This should also be fixed in v58 (duplicate issue https://github.com/flutter/flutter-intellij/issues/5615).

title: Flutter Upgrade IntelliJ Issue
